abstract: Serena Williams withdraws from Dubai Tennis Championships due to lingering respiratory illness; other tennis news and scores noted.
lead_paragraph: Williams withdrew from the Dubai Tennis Championships in the United Arab Emirates because of lingering effects of an upper respiratory illness she had last month.

headline.main: Serena Williams Withdraws from the Dubai Tennis Championships
